# =====================================================================
#  dotfiles/.gitignore
#  Defensive: even if a whole directory is ever stowed/adopted by
#  mistake, these patterns keep secrets and machine state out of git.
# =====================================================================

# --- Secrets / credentials — NEVER commit ------------------------------
**/.credentials.json
**/auth.json
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*
**/.netrc
**/hosts.yml
**/secrets*
**/*token*

# --- Per-machine local overrides ---------------------------------------
**/settings.local.json

# --- History / session / state -----------------------------------------
**/history.jsonl
**/session_index.jsonl
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite-shm
**/*.sqlite-wal
**/sessions/
**/shell-snapshots/
**/shell_snapshots/
**/projects/
**/usage-data/
**/statsig/
**/memories/
**/.last-*
**/installation_id

# --- Caches ------------------------------------------------------------
**/cache/
**/*cache*.json
**/.tmp/
**/tmp/

# --- OS / editor junk --------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
